History:
--------

I decided to make this game for these reasons:

the original Solid:

* I just simply wanted to make a game. (The original Solid)
* There didn't exist a pong clone who was simple, non commercial and didn't suck.

Solid 2:

* I wanted to make an AGA game (what is easier than remake a game that you made earlier).
* None of all pong clones had a possibility to curve balls 
* Removing all bugs of the original (It didn't work well on AGA machines)
* Maybe some other reasons I can't remember at this moment.


